data.description: Built in 2017, this immaculate corner unit home features a massive modern kitchen with oversized island, stainless steel appliances, honeycomb flooring & luxury plank flooring.Beautiful tri-level townhome in the heart of the highly sought after: Millenia.  The natural light in this unit is abundant and balcony offers ample space for a 6 seater table to enjoy San Diego's beautiful weather and the amazing breeze from the South Bay! On second level, you will find a half bath, storage closet, kitchen & living space and spacious balcony. All bedrooms are found on the third level. Master bedroom is carpeted, has a walk-in closet and a beautiful double vanity bathroom. You get beautiful views of the mountains. The third room is perfect for an office space. 2 car garage also offers plenty of storage. **See Supplemental RemarksMillenia is surrounded by a bustling area that includes the Otay Ranch Town Center and many of the conveniences you desire: parks, retail, restaurants and shops and top rated schools all around! The community offers a beautiful heated pool, playgrounds and dog parks. The house is turnkey! Don't miss out on this opportunity! Move in before the school year starts! The schools are A rated: Elementary- Wolf Canyon; Middle school-Eastlake Middle; High school -Olympian High
